The data are available for both 8-digit HUCs and EMAP hexagons and represent total species counts for each spatial unit.  More information about these resources, including the variables used in this study, may be found here: https://edg.epa.gov/data/Public/ORD/NERL/ReVA/ReVA_Data.zip.</dct:description>
